title: Hikers find large footprint along Franklin Creek.
observed: My wife and I went Franklin Creek area for hiking and we found a bigfoot track by the creek. Its about 2 miles from parking lot. We have to walk about 2 hours back to parking lot before dark and heavy rain on that night. Creek flooded and the footprint gone.
location_details: Creek, lot of forest and hills. lot of kind of mushrooms, berries and plants.
